Description:
    Generate internal Twirp API handlers and integration tests
    for Events V2 webhook payload hydration.

Arguments:
    --event-type
    # The event type which the handler will be responsible for. See a list here: https://github.com/github/hydro-schemas/blob/7950b3ac5407ee5668869a6ad02c5db013e75df5/proto/hydro/schemas/events_platform/v0/entities/event_type.proto#L23

    [--twirp-folder]
    # The folder where the Twirp API handlers will be generated. Defaults to {{EVENT_TYPE.downcase+'s'}}/webhook_payload_hydration.

Example:
    bin/rails generate webhook_payload_hydration_twirp_endpoint --event-type PULL_REQUEST_REVIEW --twirp-folder pull_requests/webhook_payload_hydration

    This will create:
    - Handler classes under:
      app/api/internal/twirp/pull_requests/webhook_payload_hydration/pull_request_review_api_handler.rb
    - Integration tests under:
      test/integration/api/internal/twirp/pull_requests/webhook_payload_hydration/pull_request_review_api_handler_test.rb
    - Mount the handler as a rack app in app/api/internal/twirp.rb
